episodes.title: Casting Extravaganza
episodes.plot: What does it really take to become America's next drag superstar? From fabulous divas to outrageous flops, RuPaul gives a behind-the-scenes look at casting for Drag Race.

episodes.title: The Queen Who Mopped X-Mas
episodes.plot: Aren't the holidays such a drag? Brighten up your night with a fierce Christmas challenge on tonight's RuPaul's Drag Race. The claws come out in the first challenge of the season when the girls are asked to create a holiday look with nothing but some tinsel, ornaments and a few well placed mistletoe.

episodes.title: Queens in Space
episodes.plot: The queens face the final frontier as they shoot two out-of-this-world sci-fi movie trailers.

episodes.title: Totally Leotarded
episodes.plot: The girls get physical as they produce their own inspirational workout videos directed by fitness guru Susan Powter.

episodes.title: QNN News
episodes.plot: The queens get a wake up call in the competition when they're asked to produce two morning news shows.

episodes.title: The Snatch Game
episodes.plot: The queens compete in a star-studded TV game show where they must pull out their best celebrity impersonations.

episodes.title: Face, Face, Face of Cakes
episodes.plot: The queens look good enough to eat in this episode where they're challenged to find fashion inspiration from the world of cakes.

episodes.title: Ru Ha Ha
episodes.plot: The queens perform stand-up comedy routines in front of a live studio audience.

episodes.title: Life, Liberty & the Pursuit of Style
episodes.plot: The queens create patriotic video messages for the troops.

episodes.title: RuPaul-a-Palooza
episodes.plot: The dolls record a single and perform before a live audience.

episodes.title: RuPaul's Hair Extravaganza
episodes.plot: The queens wig out when they have to compete in a fantasy hair show.

episodes.title: Jocks in Frocks
episodes.plot: The queens must transform a group of All-American straight jocks into their drag sisters.

episodes.title: Make Dat Money
episodes.plot: The dolls break the bank as they perform in a pageant of dresses made out of money.

episodes.title: RuPaul Rewind
episodes.plot: Take a look back at the highlights, low-lights and previously unseen footage from the first 12 episodes as we race toward the climactic grand finale.

episodes.title: Grand Finale
episodes.plot: The remaining three queens face their final challenge when they're asked to transform into video vixens for the music video to Ru's latest single, "Champion."

episodes.title: Reunited!
episodes.plot: Wigs fly as the queens return to discuss the drama of the season.
